emdawnwebgpu provides Dawn's implementation of webgpu.h for Emscripten.

To use emdawnwebgpu with Emscripten, add the following flag to emcc during both compilation and linking:

    --use-port=${CURRENT_INSTALLED_DIR}/share/emdawnwebgpu/emdawnwebgpu.port.py

For optimal code size in release builds, also use:

    --closure=1

The package provides both C and C++ headers:
- C API: #include <webgpu/webgpu.h>
- C++ API: #include <webgpu/webgpu_cpp.h>

For full usage instructions, see the README.md file:
    ${CURRENT_INSTALLED_DIR}/share/emdawnwebgpu/README.md

For more details, visit: https://github.com/google/dawn
